OOC: Oh, they'll chase her... MwahahahaHaHaHaHAHAHA!!!!!!! <choke,
choke> I'm alright...

BIC:

From the middle of the light, a huge, towering form started to rise.

???: I am Prophetus, Tripredacus Gestalt. You have chosen to be an
enemy. I shall rid our planet of your unworthiness.

The massive robot started walking at a terribly fast pace and soon was
in view of the small cat bot.

Prophetus: Hmm... I see you've transformed. Perhaps now you'll
understand what a formidable weapon your whole body has become! It is
only sorry you turned away from us... but it was your choice.

He concentrated energy for a moment and released a frightening energy
ball at her. Only, it missed. Instead of hitting her, the blast
destroyed a whole wall, revealing a passage to the surface.
